Odaily Planet Daily News: Ogle, consultant of Trump family crypto project WLFI, posted on X platform that he was hated by so many people when he shorted Celsius a few years ago. Hereby clarify: 
1. WLFI and Meme coin TRUMP are independent projects, which should be clear now; 
2. I am a long-term supporter of the TRUMP team. They are very reliable and will do cool things; 
3. There is no insider trading information in the past and now. In fact, the transaction pointed out occurred after the farce between Trump and Musk because of holding a large number of TRUMP token positions; 
4. If there is indeed insider information, I will not trade for ethical reasons. Even if there is no other reason, there have been such experiences in the past and they are well documented; 
5. You can hedge your long positions by shorting to hedge against price fluctuations.
